data.description: Simply the best and lowest priced home that is in turnkey, move-in condition and totally gorgeous. Don't miss this one level home, with updated modern finishes and amazing style. From the stained concrete floors, to the sliding doors, to the exquisite lighting. This home is sure to please all. Book a showing today before it is gone. The home is centrally located in Wailuku Town. Walk to everything including first Fridays. Close to restaurants, shopping, and downtown Wailuku. Part of the Wailuku Redevelopment Zone, so you can to vacation rental at this property if you are only here part-time. Could also be used as commercial space due to zoning. Have a live/work home if you prefer. This is such a wonderful specialty zoned home. Newer appliances, newer washer dryer, newer concrete floors, keyless entry. There is a custom barn door with a wireless flat screen tv mounted right on the door! Two car parking, plus two hour parking for clients/friends on Maluhia Drive. You can walk to Market Street via a short cut behind the Iao Theater to partake in First Friday.
